org.opends.server.backends.jeb.importLDIF

Class ImportIDSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.server.backends.jeb.importLDIF.ImportIDSet

  • public class ImportIDSet
extends java.lang.Object
    This class manages the set of ID that are to be eventually added to an index database. It is responsible for determining if the number of IDs is above the configured ID limit. If the limit it reached, the class stops tracking individual IDs and marks the set as undefined. This class is not thread safe.
